DeckBrew,is,a,website,for,building,Magic,The,Gathering,MTG,decks,Although,the,website,is,still,under,development,it,already,has,a,functional,API,for,retrieving,information,on,MTG,cards,This,information,includes,a,listing,of,all,MTG,cards,listings,of,cards,from,a,given,multiverse,set,or,color,details,on,a,single,card,etc,All,textual,information,presented,through,the,API,belongs,to,Wizards,of,the,Coast,The,DeckBrew,API,is,still,in,beta,and,changes,may,be,made,at,any,time